description: Navigate to Woolworths Town Hall. Enter Town Hall station and proceed straight through the underground concourse, keeping the ticket gates and vending machines on your right. Ascend the stairs marked with a green Woolworths sign to exit the station. The destination is the Woolworths building located at street level immediately after exiting.
